00:25:14.040 --> 00:25:15.900
So no, I wasn't able
to speak with Arneson.

00:25:15.900 --> 00:25:17.424
Naturally, I read
a lot of his work,

00:25:17.424 --> 00:25:19.090
and saw a lot of
